headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Buying Morgan Stanley (MS) After Its Strong Multi Year Rally
summary: If you are wondering whether Morgan Stanley is still good value after a strong multi year run, this article will walk through what the current share price might be implying about its worth. The stock recently closed at US$176.68, with a 1 year return of 32.3% and a 5 year return of 174.8%, even as the share price shows a 1.9% pullback over 7 days, a 5.3% decline over 30 days, and a 2.9% decline year to date. headline: Morgan Stanley now expects 2026 PC shipments to decline more than 5% YoY
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley now expects global PC shipments to fall by more than 5% in 2026 after what analyst Erik Woodring called “the biggest monthly miss since April ’22” in January notebook builds.
